#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Handle all your customers in a breeze and get a nice overview of your income "
"through the reporting features that are integrated in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Z lahkoto upravljajte z vsemi svojimi strankami in si zagotovite lep pregled "
"nad svojimi prihodki s pomočjo funkcij poročanja, ki so integrirane v Odoo."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can invoice your presence to your customer through the "
"invoice app. You can configure your invoice templates to include terms &amp; "
"conditions, as well as other handy features."
msgstr ""
"Če je primerno, lahko stranki izstavite račun za svojo prisotnost prek "
"aplikacije za račune. Predloge računov lahko konfigurirate tako, da "
"vključujejo pogoje in določila ter druge priročne funkcije."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can of course directly manage your events directly in the "
"Field service app without going through the CRM and Sales app."
msgstr ""
"Če je primerno, lahko seveda svoje dogodke upravljate neposredno v "
"aplikaciji Terenska služba, ne da bi morali uporabljati aplikacijo CRM in "
"Prodaja."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to easily discover every features of this package, try "
"downloading the Demo Data."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preprosto odkriti vse funkcije tega paketa, poskusite prenesti "
"demo podatke."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In some cases, you will get bookings from customers (coporate, etc.) for you "
"to attend an company event or other similar events."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih primerih boste prejeli rezervacije strank (podjetniških itd.) za "
"udeležbo na poslovnem dogodku ali drugih podobnih dogodkih."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Incoming opportunities can be registered into your CRM. Manage opportunity "
"stages in the kanban view, categorization using tags, to-do's and reminders "
"using activities, and communication through the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Prihodne priložnosti je mogoče registrirati v vašem CRM-ju. Upravljajte faze "
"priložnosti v pogledu kanban, kategorizacijo z oznakami, opravila in "
"opomnike z dejavnostmi ter komunikacijo prek klepeta."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Install the <strong>Social Marketing App </strong>to manage your social "
"media presence."
msgstr ""
"Namestite <strong>aplikacijo Družbeni marketing </strong>za upravljanje "
"svoje prisotnosti na družbenih omrežjih."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice your customers using the <strong>Invoice app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Izstavite račune svojim strankam z <strong>Aplikacijo za račune</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoicing Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentacija za izdajanje računov"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Just be careful, once demo data are uploaded, it cannot be easily deleted. "
"But you can restart a fresh database on"
msgstr ""
"Bodite previdni, ko so demo podatki naloženi, jih ni mogoče enostavno "
"izbrisati. Lahko pa znova zaženete novo bazo podatkov na"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Manage your <strong>Purchases and Inventory</strong> in Odoo as well."
msgstr "Upravljajte svoje <strong>Nabavo in Zaloge</strong> tudi v Odooju."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your presence at events using the <strong>Field Service app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte svojo prisotnost na dogodkih z aplikacijo <strong>Terenska "
"storitev</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_7
msgid "Multi-Day"
msgstr "Več dnevni"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Need a Website? No problem, Odoo can do it as well."
msgstr "Potrebujete spletno stran? Ni problema, tudi to lahko stori Odoo."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo.com/trial"
msgstr "Odoo.com/trial"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you have all the information regarding this opportunity, you can make a "
"new quotation. Define how long you'll be staying, and if relevant, other "
"things you will be charging to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Ko boste imeli vse informacije o tej priložnosti, lahko pripravite novo "
"ponudbo. Določite, kako dolgo boste ostali, in če je ustrezno, še druge "
"stroške, ki jih boste zaračunali stranki."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Point of Sale Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentacija prodajnega mesta"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Kontaktirajte nas"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Sales Documentation"
msgstr "Prodajna dokumentacija"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Send quotations to prospective customers through the <strong>Sales app</"
"strong>"
msgstr ""
"Pošljite ponudbe potencialnim strankam preko <strong>aplikacije za Prodajo</"
"strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take a look at the <strong>Email Marketing App</strong> to let past "
"customers know what you're up to !"
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si <strong>aplikacijo za E-poštno trženje</strong> in obvestite "
"pretekle stranke, kaj počnete!"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use the <strong>CRM app</strong> to manage your opportunities"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <strong>CRM aplikacijo</strong> za upravljanje vaših priložnosti"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When your prospective customer confirms the sale, a new task is created in "
"your field service app, and linked back to your sale order. You can manage "
"assignations, needs, and so on from there and obtain a handy overview of "
"your\n"
"        planning."
msgstr ""
"Ko vaša potencialna stranka potrdi prodajo, se v vaši aplikaciji Field "
"Service ustvari nova naloga, ki je povezana z vašim prodajnim naročilom. Tam "
"lahko upravljate dodelitve, potrebe in tako naprej ter dobite priročen "
"pregled nad svojim \n"
"        načrtovanjem."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While on the field, you can take orders and payments from your customers or "
"from the attendees through the Point of Sale app. The app is a fully "
"featured point-of-sale solution that supports menus, products, quantities, "
"discounts,\n"
"        pricelists, custom notes, and many other features."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko ste na terenu, lahko prek aplikacije POS sprejemate naročila in "
"plačila od svojih strank ali udeležencev. Aplikacija je celovita rešitev za "
"POS, ki podpira menije, izdelke, količine, popuste,\n"
"        cenike, opombe po meri in številne druge funkcije."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the Food Trucks Industry Package, you have all you need to manage your "
"business from customer bookings to invoicing, including a point-of-sale "
"system and much more."
msgstr ""
"S paketom Food Trucks Industry Package imate vse, kar potrebujete za "
"upravljanje svojega podjetja, od rezervacij strank do izstavljanja računov, "
"vključno s sistemom prodajnih mest in še veliko več."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"Bi se radi z nami pogovorili o svoji nastavitvi Odoo ali raziskali več "
"funkcij?"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can still do it by upgrading your package in Apps."
msgstr ""
"To lahko še vedno storite tako, da nadgradite svoj paket v Aplikacijah."

